  "description": "This image captures a breathtaking sunset over a coastal landscape. The sky is ablaze with vibrant, layered clouds in shades of fiery orange, deep red, and soft pink. These clouds stretch horizontally across the frame, creating a dramatic and textured sky. A distant, hazy mountain range is visible on the horizon, silhouetted against the bright orange glow. Below the mountains, a body of water reflects the colors of the sky, creating a mirrored effect. The foreground is composed of dark, silhouetted trees and foliage, providing a grounding element to the expansive sky. The overall impression is one of natural beauty and tranquility.",
